{"tid":488623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院判非緊急情況　警查被捕者手機須手令　律政司不服提上訴","createTime":"2017-12-04T01:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T10:57:04.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b771541936419cf29547de92f961e5c4e3c006","tid":488623,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T01:30:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高院判非緊急情況　警查被捕者手機須手令　律政司不服提上訴</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n警方於2014年七一遊行期間，拘捕民陣5名成員並沒收手機，負責為遊行隊伍駕駛開路車的司機岑永根認為，警方沒收其手機違反《基本法》及《香港人權法案條例》，提出司法覆核勝訴。岑永根向傳媒稱，律政司不服判決，在上訴期限前提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n高院法官10月頒下判詞，裁定警員只能在緊急情況下，才可在沒有手令下檢查被捕人士手機的數碼內容，但相關《警隊條例》條文不違憲。<br />\n<br />\n岑永根向《蘋果日報》稱，袁國強於上月24日、即政府提出上訴期限最後一日前，就高院上述裁決提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n《信報》引述消息指出，律政司指出高院原訟庭法官區慶祥錯誤解釋《警隊條例》第50（6）條，只賦予警方在緊急情況下，才可在沒有搜查令下，搜查手提電話、平板電腦、智能手錶、手提電腦等類似器材的數碼內容，律政司認為只要有合理懷疑，警方為有助調查，可毋須手令搜查涉嫌人士的相關數碼內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/高院判非緊急情況-警查被捕者手機須手令-律政司不服提上訴/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E5%88%A4%E9%9D%9E%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81-%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%A0%88%E6%89%8B%E4%BB%A4-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%2F&d=ZZPNaLy14umPRrz0OKTL26WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ef96aa39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E5%88%A4%E9%9D%9E%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81-%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%A0%88%E6%89%8B%E4%BB%A4-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%2F&h=b4f191ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/高院判非緊急情況-警查被捕者手機須手令-律政司不服提上訴/</a>"},{"pid":"3d1d0c8edf058d993ea969664d51c6f982b485da","tid":488623,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f21933718bbc19c617ec309bacdad20c8154f1","tid":488623,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c4797fcdd84007bf9258cb200da9483faad3a2","tid":488623,"uid":3223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"提醒返， ios 5下power 制會 disable touch id/face id"},{"pid":"1e30774ef4c0d478eac8f36762673f3859b90336","tid":488623,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4dae59a14cf6b5c2add0e6cbb46c501e0bd8f3","tid":488623,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>提醒返， ios 5下power 制會 disable touch id/face id</blockquote><br />\n學到野"}]}